<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mew1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mew</orth> (cf. <emph>Emmew</emph>) to shut up, to confine: <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.132" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 132</bibl>. With <cit><quote>up:</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 1.1.87" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 1, 87</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.1.87" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 1, 87</bibl> <bibl n="shak. jn 4.2.57" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 2, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.38" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.139" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 139</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.4.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 4, 11</bibl> <emph>(to-night she is --ed up to her heaviness).</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>